          <h2 id="why-toronto">Why You Need a Sump Pump in Toronto</h2>
          <p>A sump pump is your basement's first line of defense against water damage. Here in Toronto, with our high water tables and extreme weather events, a properly installed sump pump system is essential for:</p>
          
          <ul class="benefits-list">
            <li>Preventing basement flooding during heavy rains and spring thaw</li>
